title: What it Takes to Be Great
itunes:title: What it Takes to Be Great
description:
I believe that everyone can be great at one thing in their life and I believe it is our obligation to find our own greatness. In this episode, I will teach you what it takes to be great!

Watch my inspiration YouTube videos here: https://www.youtube.com/robdialjr
